again.

05:18.419 --> 05:20.921
I need your...
skinny little arms.

05:20.954 --> 05:22.356
Oh.

05:22.390 --> 05:23.391
Did you shake it?

05:23.424 --> 05:26.326
Yeah, I shook it,
I shook it.

05:29.897 --> 05:32.466
We have such
a roller coaster thing,

05:32.500 --> 05:33.534
Karen and I.

05:33.567 --> 05:35.369
Excuse me?

05:35.403 --> 05:36.837
Roller-coastery friendship.

05:36.870 --> 05:39.373
Hot and cold.
On again, off again.

05:39.407 --> 05:42.743
Sexual-tension-filled
type of deal.

05:42.776 --> 05:44.945
It's very Sam and Diane.

05:44.978 --> 05:46.947
Wow.
From Cheers.

05:46.980 --> 05:48.115
Yep.
Yeah.

05:48.148 --> 05:50.451
And another thing about
the Indian people,

05:50.484 --> 05:52.386
they love sex positions.

05:52.420 --> 05:55.923
I present to you
The Kama Sutra.

05:55.956 --> 05:58.692
I mean, look at that.
Who has seen that before?

05:58.726 --> 06:01.495
I have, that's
the union of the monkey.

06:01.529 --> 06:03.831
Oh, that's
what they call it.

06:03.864 --> 06:05.833
This is the best meeting
we have ever had.

06:05.866 --> 06:06.667
