07:19.973 --> 07:22.510
Isn't this fun,
not wearing shoes?

07:22.543 --> 07:24.177
I wish some of us still
had our shoes on.

07:24.211 --> 07:26.714
Stop it.
It's a disease.

07:26.747 --> 07:28.448
I've...told you.

07:30.017 --> 07:33.220
I thought you said
this was a costume party.

07:34.922 --> 07:37.090
