07:42.029 --> 07:43.731
Hey, Kevin,
it's a costume.

07:43.764 --> 07:45.933
You just cool it, okay?

07:45.966 --> 07:47.234
Carol? Carol.

07:49.870 --> 07:50.938
I'll have one of those
as well.

07:50.971 --> 07:52.105
Thank you very much.

07:52.139 --> 07:53.974
Now, these are limes,
lemons, onions.

07:54.007 --> 07:56.143
I'm a vegetarian.
What can I eat?

07:56.176 --> 07:58.512
