08:14.562 --> 08:15.729
These s'mores
are disgusting.

08:15.763 --> 08:19.132
They're not s'mores.
They're samosas.

08:20.734 --> 08:22.736
Do you think
they have any s'mores?

08:22.770 --> 08:25.606
All they are is chocolate,
graham cracker, and marshmallow.

08:25.639 --> 08:27.274
