about Zach Braff.

08:49.697 --> 08:50.998
Don't even listen to them.

08:51.031 --> 08:52.633
No, you know...

08:54.101 --> 08:56.103
That's very official.

08:56.136 --> 08:57.204
I decided to come.

08:57.237 --> 09:00.608
Uh, I feel a little
underdressed.

09:00.641 --> 09:02.342
But at least
I'm not dressed

09:02.375 --> 09:04.712
like a slutty cheerleader,
right?

09:04.745 --> 09:06.246
Is that mean?

09:06.279 --> 09:09.249
[Indian music]

09:09.282 --> 09:17.290
