the kind of thing

11:04.798 --> 11:05.966
where when you die,

11:05.999 --> 11:07.968
she has to throw herself
on fire?

11:08.001 --> 11:09.837
No?

11:09.870 --> 11:11.171
Okay.

11:11.204 --> 11:13.106
