[splat]

11:23.884 --> 11:24.852
Ooh!

11:24.885 --> 11:27.855
[Indian music]

11:27.888 --> 11:33.093
*

11:33.126 --> 11:36.096
Are you okay?

11:36.129 --> 11:38.832
